================================================================================
Vasnecov (v. 1.1.3)
================================================================================

Simple C++/Qt wrapper for OpenGL-based 3D graphics.

================================================================================

It uses Qt Graphics View Framework for rendering. Qt5 is required.

Main abilities:
 - Controlling scene objects from other threads;
 - Preparing a viewport (Universe) with several scenes (Worlds);
 - Creating and manipulation scene elements with tree-structure;
 - Using diffuse materials with textures (from QImage) and lights for shading;
 - Drawing simple figures by point-to-point method;
 - Typing text and raster images at billboards (labels);
 - Loading meshes from Wavefront OBJ format.
 - Order sorting for transparent objects.
